p8_TYPE=Integer
p8_default_value=31
p8_description=Upper limit for RAM allocated to indexing process, in Gbyte. For very large genomes you might heve to increase this, but make sure that the RAM is indeed physically present on the server and you have permission to make it available for the process. 
